name: Shasta College
directions:
The college has a few single stall bathrooms available for any gender on campus. They are in buildings all around campus. The one in the 100 building is right across from the business office (more towards the back of the building). 
The exact location for the rest of the listed bathrooms is not exact, but they should be easy enough to find: 
200 building
300 building
1300 building
2000 building
2100 building
2400 building
2500 building
2600 building
3200 building
3500 building
4000 building
Hopefully this list will be updated in the future to include exact directions to the other listed bathrooms. The link below will take you to a map of the campus.
http://www.shastacollege.edu/Resources/PDF/Campus%20Map%20Redding%20Main.pdf
comment: The 3200, 3500, and 4000 building are not necessarily accessible to everyone and are degree specific buildings.
